{"about_the_game":"Maldrin Journey is a 3D Collectathon adventure game, currently being developed in the Unity game engine. Which contains two main modes of play. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe first is a single player story mode, where the objective is to explore 16 open levels to find the scattered artefacts to save the shrine guardians, each level also features:<br />\r\n <br />\r\nTen artefacts, hidden in various locations as a reward for completing challenges.<br />\r\nCoins, which can be used to get hints on where the artefacts are.<br />\r\nA secret artefact, only one of these hidden in each level. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe artefacts are used to progress through the story.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe second is a split screen two player racing mode, where the objective is to collect more coins and artefacts then your competitor along with finishing the stage first. The winner is the best out of the three categories.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nBoth modes of play allow players to test their platforming and exploration skills to save the day or beat their rivals in a split screen race.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPlease note: A controller is recommended for playing Maldrin Journey. Two player mode requires at least one controller.","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"A New Adventure Begins","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1070400/3944a492c9c633ef2e5aae2cb5d88e9fa1e2e68e.jpg"},{"name":"One Of Many","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1070400/69e58cae6053f6b03defd65447a6eaebea6d06c8.jpg"},{"name":"Good Eyes","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1070400/02336524e8724a57e19e3a9b8b6286a8066eaef1.jpg"},{"name":"Hyper Rescued","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1070400/88e655e7e97b18abb39905324b5e67f02319d693.jpg"},{"name":"Swift Rescued","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1070400/9e93c4165